{"layout":"logicalStructure","root":{"data":{"text":"<p>Azure DevOps Server 域迁移</p>","expand":true,"uid":"ca0503f6-f9f1-41db-8e6a-6fb10e66afca","richText":true,"isActive":false,"imgMap":{"smm_img_key_9105812b-dc35-4d1f-afd6-e2dad972195f":"data:image/png;base64,"}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>权限准备</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"b70ce034-8a13-4446-832d-bc10dc3e538d","generalization":[{"text":"<p>这个迁移账号，不能是未来要迁移的账号</p>","range":[0,3],"uid":"241c4cec-4995-4556-90d0-ed0658118871","richText":true,"isActive":false,"expand":true}]},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>AT 服务器：<strong>Local Administrators</strong></p>","uid":"70328957-f6ba-4d61-afeb-dc58170fb27c","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Azure DevOps Server：Team Foundation Administrators</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"e3ec42ac-ed1d-4975-82a6-f7d94a06732f"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>SQL Server：sysadmin</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"ef14e713-6e63-46c9-ab63-01a0faf38bfe"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Reporting（如有）：管理权限</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"689f3d1f-bd52-4692-8910-17db20c57286"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>核查成员</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"8b4b7e9d-19d8-42a3-91e9-6f283bf2d109"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>从 Local Administrators 组移除待迁移账号（注意：每台 AT 都需执行）</p>","uid":"858b2cdb-75f8-408b-bcf2-d939db843a87","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>核对身份，枚举当前 ADO Identity 表：<strong>TFSConfig Identities</strong>（在 AT 执行）</p>","uid":"b57960ee-0ab6-47e1-9449-b24440f5c8f2","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"%ProgramFiles%\\Microsoft Visual Studio 12.0 Team Foundation Server\\Tools"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>Users</p>","uid":"926bdb44-8dc7-422b-9ea8-c6cb3d3a9421","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Groups</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"ccb97bd7-dae4-49a4-a858-ab0d988084aa"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Service Accounts</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"09696cf2-f640-47ed-ac4f-7576aaf3d402"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>创建 Identity Mapping 表（官方建议）</p><p>old=&gt;new (domain/account)</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"09f6e27a-fb83-4ea7-8fae-b4c59dd60c6f"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>停止 ADO 服务（防止在迁移过程中产生新的数据）</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"653a7641-083e-44eb-8181-947a0bee8df5"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>在 AT 执行：<strong>TFSServiceControl quiesce</strong></p>","uid":"a7a8cf88-7138-40e7-921c-8f5e81665697","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"Drive:\\\\%programfiles%\\\\TFS 12.0\\\\Tools"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>备份数据库、SQL Server Reporting Services encryption key</p>","generalization":[],"uid":"08b337c7-121e-4e6d-b3c8-6c56089caef8","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"customTextWidth":511},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>Configuration</p>","uid":"ea37a588-7a13-4975-bd02-9d3aa3547359","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Collection</p>","uid":"2b8ba816-83e5-4a5b-89f3-6e76f72ce4b1","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Warehouse DB、Analysis DB、Reporting Encryption Key（SSRS）</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"85bbaf23-1c88-462e-99dd-7b7b6317467d"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Application Tier 加入新域（重启）</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"79c8a5bb-e081-4874-86fc-20ff41659c5b"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>AT</p>","uid":"37a05a58-d6ad-4953-b6e9-32a2ea0eba67","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Proxy</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"a12fce4e-dca0-4653-a63c-9efa0a30b0e0"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Reporting Server</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"1c34122c-30a4-48f3-a345-92de1b84a219"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Identity Migration（SID Mapping）</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"c8c824f8-d0b0-4040-b90d-674f9e8b7b4a"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>账号名称一致：TFSConfig Identities /change /fromdomain:OldDomainName /todomain:NewDomainName</p>","uid":"aaa2dd8b-44ff-46cd-9a87-b092fd06ee13","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>账号名称不一致（需要逐个改）：TFSConfig Identities /change /fromdomain:OldDomainName /todomain:NewDomainName /account:OldAccountName /toaccount:NewAccountName</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"54ace871-d278-43f9-b5d1-73fefa2f71ba"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Service Account：TFSConfig Accounts /change /AccountType:ApplicationTier /account:AccountName /password:Password</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"da530bee-df38-43e5-aa3c-a22a85dfd599"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Reporting Account（如果有）：TFSConfig Accounts /change /AccountType:ReportingDataSource /account:AccountName /password:Password</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"1fc85079-cfe5-4a3f-91e1-d954d9eb4f5c"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Proxy Account（如果有）：TFSConfig Accounts /change /AccountType:Proxy /account:AccountName /password:Password</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"1943e3a3-9db4-4c75-92dc-f771b66d914a"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>NT AUTHORITY\\NETWORK SERVICE：两阶段</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"c559e515-dc77-4690-9c09-c59e1105e4ef"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>旧域中的无效账号</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"afec675b-84b3-43b9-8a77-4f673ac66710"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><br></p>","uid":"60b3b783-7c1b-43cf-9c2a-7f7e12b92aa7","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"image":"smm_img_key_9105812b-dc35-4d1f-afd6-e2dad972195f","imageTitle":"","imageSize":{"width":353,"height":299,"custom":false}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Reporting 修复（如使用）</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"e3e06915-c717-401a-83ed-22a3b89f09f1"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>Admin Console</p>","uid":"d0d64c67-f14f-4e88-984a-c27d0515cd10","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"- Reporting Server URL\n- Analysis Service\n- Data Source Account"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>✅ Start Jobs ✅ Rebuild Warehouse</p>","uid":"77d48c7f-520b-4aff-8b1e-8ab9eb2ddee2","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>Backup Plan 修复</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"0a6b5cc7-5ff9-4c42-bc52-e32ce43af067"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>- Network Share 变更</p><p>- 存储路径变更</p>","uid":"551fd17d-c2a5-4031-9a4e-f378cf7f2112","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>恢复服务</p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"f3d4b8ae-65ad-49c8-8428-6112c84c5250"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>TFSServiceControl unquiesce</p>","uid":"a0a59d41-3a9b-4200-a3b3-63b44eb12921","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]}]},"theme":{"template":"classic4","config":{}},"view":{"transform":{"scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"shear":0,"rotate":0,"translateX":-1023,"translateY":-236,"originX":0,"originY":0,"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"e":-1023,"f":-236},"state":{"scale":1,"x":-1023,"y":-236,"sx":-1104,"sy":-467}}}